title: 2019 Week 8 Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 8 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dave Hanzus, Mack Sessler, Curtis Wesseling and Craig Rosenthal preview each game leading into week 8 including some heated medical talk. Can the Cardinals take down the Saints? (25:35) Is this a must win game for the Jets against the Jags? (37:29)
